query: SELECT dusun from kartu_ibu_registration where userID='user12' group by dusun

SELECT kartu_ibu_registration.dusun as desa, count(*) as linfas_bulan_lalu FROM kartu_pnc_dokumentasi_persalinan inner join kartu_anc_visit on kartu_anc_visit.motherid = kartu_pnc_dokumentasi_persalinan.motherid inner join kartu_ibu_registration on kartu_ibu_registration.kiid = kartu_anc_visit.kiid where kartu_ibu_registration.userid =  'user12' and kartu_pnc_dokumentasi_persalinan.tempatBersalin !='-' and kartu_pnc_dokumentasi_persalinan.submissionDate between '2015-01-01' and '2015-10-31' group by kartu_ibu_registration.dusun

SELECT kartu_ibu_registration.dusun as desa, count(*) as linfas_bulan_ini FROM kartu_pnc_dokumentasi_persalinan inner join kartu_anc_visit on kartu_anc_visit.motherid = kartu_pnc_dokumentasi_persalinan.motherid inner join kartu_ibu_registration on kartu_ibu_registration.kiid = kartu_anc_visit.kiid where kartu_ibu_registration.userid =  'user12' and kartu_pnc_dokumentasi_persalinan.tempatBersalin !='-' and kartu_pnc_dokumentasi_persalinan.submissionDate between '2015-11-01' and '2015-11-31' group by kartu_ibu_registration.dusun

SELECT kartu_ibu_registration.dusun as desa, count(*) as kunjungan_bulan_lalu FROM kartu_pnc_visit inner join kartu_ibu_registration on kartu_ibu_registration.kiid = kartu_pnc_visit.kiid where kartu_ibu_registration.userid =  'user12' and kartu_pnc_visit.clientVersionSubmissionDate between '2015-01-01' and '2015-10-31' group by kartu_ibu_registration.dusun

SELECT kartu_ibu_registration.dusun as desa, count(*) as kunjungan_bulan_ini FROM kartu_pnc_visit inner join kartu_ibu_registration on kartu_ibu_registration.kiid = kartu_pnc_visit.kiid where kartu_ibu_registration.userid =  'user12' and kartu_pnc_visit.clientVersionSubmissionDate between '2015-11-01' and '2015-11-31' group by kartu_ibu_registration.dusun
